# Next.js Project Component Usage Cursor Rule

This cursor rule defines the allowed components for use in this Next.js project. The components are sourced from HeroUI (imported from `@heroui/react`), React Bits (imported from `@/components/ReactBits`), and Lucide React Icons (imported from `lucide-react`). For every allowed component, please refer to its official documentation for usage guidelines. Any component not listed below should be treated as a standard HTML element.

---

## Project Framework
- This is a Next.js project using the App Router.  
- For generic page building (standard layout and structure), use standard HTML elements unless explicitly specified to use a HeroUI or React Bits component.

